        </button>
        <button class="apn-s-subgap-btn" data-subgap="duration" onclick="apnSleepSelectSubgap(this)">
          Duration: I do not get enough hours
          <span>Your schedule, commitments, or habits cut your window short. Less than 7 hours consistently means your testosterone synthesis cycle cannot complete and your GH pulse window is compressed.</span>
        </button>
